
                               TOTAL ECLIPSE
                               -------------

                    Edited by Parasite and Codetapper!


You can use the joystick and mouse or the keyboard.


KEYBOARD CONTROLS
-----------------
Move forward:       Cursor up
Move backward:      Cursor down
Turn left:          Left cursor
Turn right:         Right cursor
U-turn:             U
Step length:        S
Crouch/stand:       H
Change angle:       A
Look up:            P
Look down:          L
Face forward:       F
Flashlight on/off:  T
Rest (hold down)    R (calms the heart)
Sights on/off:      Space bar
Tilt left:          N
Tilt right:         M
Fire gun:           0
Music toggle:       +
Interrupt play:     I (save, load and abort)
